title: Sweet Chilli Pork Meatballs & Soy Veggies with Garlic Cauliflower Rice
description: Sweet chilli is an all-time favourite flavour combo, turn it into a glaze and slather it over pork meatballs for a tasty dinner. If you have any glaze left it will be soaked up in a fragrant cauliflower rice.

